    :answer_a: XML
    :answer_b: JSON
    :correct: a
    :feedback_a: JSON is simpler and more directly maps to native data structures we already have in programming languages, the parsing and data extraction code is usually simpler and more direct when using JSON.
    :feedback_b: XML is more self descriptive than JSON, but does not have the simpler and more direct mapping that JSON has.

